		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This is actually could be done as a raycaster to allow more freedom on the movements, basically Wolf3D turned 90 degree.<br /><br />I also had an idea of a low-spec first person Mario done exactly the same way. It would have quite blocky graphics for pipes, but it is certainly possible.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
