	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The title screen to Gunstar Heroes on the Genesis <span style="font-size: 85%; line-height: normal">(and Tongueman's Logic too...)</span> uses the same technique to make flat tilemaps appear to be a 3-D box; other games &amp; demos do it too.  Not <em>too</em> computationally-intensive.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


